<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Login Verification - <%= ORG_NAME %></title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f8fafc; color: #1e293b; }
    .wrapper { max-width: 600px; margin: 40px auto; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 16px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 10px 25px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05), 0 8px 10px -6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); }
    .logo-container { padding: 32px 0 24px; text-align: center; }
    .logo { font-size: 28px; font-weight: 800; color: #2563eb; letter-spacing: -1px; text-transform: uppercase; }
    .banner { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2563eb 0%, #1e40af 100%); padding: 32px 24px; text-align: left; position: relative; }
    .banner-content { color: #ffffff; }
    .banner-title { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; margin: 0; }
    .banner-icon { position: absolute; right: 24px; top: 50%; transform: translateY(-50%); opacity: 0.2; }
    .content { padding: 40px 32px; }
    .greeting { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 8px; color: #0f172a; }
    .description { font-size: 15px; color: #64748b; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 32px; }
    .otp-label { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; color: #94a3b8; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .otp-container { background: #eff6ff; border: 1px solid #dbeafe; border-radius: 12px; padding: 24px; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 32px; }
    .otp-value { font-size: 42px; font-weight: 800; color: #1e40af; letter-spacing: 12px; font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace; margin: 0; padding-left: 12px; }
    .validity { font-size: 14px; color: #94a3b8; margin-top: 24px; }
    .security-box { background-color: #f8fafc; border-radius: 12px; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #f1f5f9; margin-bottom: 32px; }
    .security-title { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: #0f172a; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .security-text { font-size: 13px; color: #64748b; line-height: 1.5; margin: 0; }
    .regards { font-size: 15px; color: #334155; margin-bottom: 40px; }
    .regards span { display: block; font-weight: 700; color: #1e40af; margin-top: 4px; }
    .footer { background-color: #fbfeff; padding: 40px 32px; text-align: center; border-top: 1px solid #f1f5f9; }
    .app-buttons { margin-bottom: 32px; }
    .app-btn { display: inline-block; margin: 0 6px; }
    .footer-text { font-size: 12px; color: #94a3b8; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 24px; max-width: 480px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; }
    .footer-links { margin-bottom: 24px; }
    .footer-link { font-size: 13px; color: #2563eb; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; margin: 0 12px; }
    .social-icons { margin-top: 16px; }
    .social-icon { display: inline-block; width: 32px; height: 32px; margin: 0 8px; opacity: 0.6; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="logo-container">
      <div class="logo">🐟 <%= ORG_NAME %></div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="banner">
      <div class="banner-content">
        <h2 class="banner-title"><%= ORG_NAME %> - Login Verification OTP</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="banner-icon">
        <svg width="60" height="60" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="white">
          <path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm0 3c1.66 0 3 1.34 3 3s-1.34 3-3 3-3-1.34-3-3 1.34-3 3-3zm0 14.2c-2.5 0-4.71-1.28-6-3.22.03-1.99 4-3.08 6-3.08 1.99 0 5.97 1.09 6 3.08-1.29 1.94-3.5 3.22-6 3.22z"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <p class="greeting">Dear <%= name %>,</p>
      <p class="description">Your one time password (OTP) for Login is:</p>
      
      <div class="otp-container">
        <p class="otp-label">Security Verification Code</p>
        <p class="otp-value"><%= otp %></p>
      </div>

      <p class="validity">This OTP is valid for <strong>2 minutes</strong>.</p>
      
      <div class="security-box">
        <h4 class="security-title">🛡️ Security Tip:</h4>
        <p class="security-text">
          Please do not share this OTP with anyone else. If you did not request this OTP, please change your password immediately or contact our support team.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="regards">
        Warm Regards,<br>
        <span>Team <%= ORG_NAME %></span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <div class="app-buttons">
         <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/3/3c/Download_on_the_App_Store_Badge.svg" alt="App Store" width="120" class="app-btn">
         <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/7/78/Google_Play_Store_badge_EN.svg" alt="Google Play" width="135" class="app-btn">
      </div>
      
      <p class="footer-text">
        Disclaimer: <%= ORG_NAME %> will never ask for personal details, passwords or OTPs outside its official platform. Stay vigilant and protect your account from suspicious activity.
      </p>

      <div class="footer-links">
        <a href="#" class="footer-link">Support</a>
        <a href="#" class="footer-link">Privacy Policy</a>
        <a href="#" class="footer-link">Terms of Service</a>
      </div>

      <div class="social-icons">
        <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/5/51/Facebook_f_logo_%282019%29.svg" alt="FB" width="24" class="social-icon">
        <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/c/ce/X_logo_2023.svg" alt="X" width="20" class="social-icon">
        <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/c/ca/LinkedIn_logo_initials.png" alt="IN" width="24" class="social-icon">
      </div>
      
      <p style="font-size: 11px; color: #94a3b8; margin-top: 32px;">
        © 2026 <%= ORG_NAME %>. All rights reserved.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
